ue entre diverses traditions, faisant appel aux meilleurs courants de plusieurs philosophies pour développer un point de vue unique ». - Gaëlle Fiasse, Université McGill  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 26. Apr 2024) 0aExperience. 0aHuman behavior. 0aIdentity (Psychology). 0aLife change events. 0aLife. 0aSelf. 0aSpontaneity (Personality trait). 7aPHILOSOPHY / General.2bisacsh1 aLambert, Pierrot, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Complete eBook-Package 2020z978311127253508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2020z978311127473740uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9782763749815423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9782763749815/original  a978-3-11-127253-5  ACUP Complete eBook-Package 2020b2020  a978-3-11-127473-7  ACUP Upgrade eBook-Package 2020b2020  aGBV-deGruyter-alles